title: Tether declares victory in class action lawsuit as judge dismisses case
description:
Tether declared a legal victory on Aug. 4 as it reported that a class action suit concerning its USDT stablecoin had been dismissed in court. The case began in December 2021 when plaintiffs Matthew Anderson and Shawn Dolifka made allegations about USDT’s backing. This was based on findings from the New York Attorney General (NYAG) […]
